{"tid":507994,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[孝子]杭州好唔好玩?","createTime":"2017-12-23T19:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T17:13:24.000Z","uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b27049d0484f4e816e8c2f88bb86a9a5a3fce638","tid":507994,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"同老母去<br />\n4日3夜<br />\n<br />\n有冇酒店推薦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8b20d3e823b95c14dc21954b55feb2fcb773fe","tid":507994,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3866dc84201edbae53fc5dd3846acce52f31b995","tid":507994,"uid":25800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b27049d0484f4e816e8c2f88bb86a9a5a3fce638","tid":507994,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"同老母去<br />\n4日3夜<br />\n<br />\n有冇酒店推薦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T20:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/044958_c54df297b128c5bf584e3706ce170b18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F044958_c54df297b128c5bf584e3706ce170b18.png&h=6f7c3603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推薦呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留意返杭州有啲酒店好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲剩係招待大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時咁岩book左一間唔招待外國人同香港<br />\n搞左好耐先book到呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢間真心正 又近附近啲景點<br />\n一落樓下就係清河坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境又唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有得免費洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0be8601792233d5c30a0b6d3dd74458e01cf327","tid":507994,"uid":41908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T21:06:01.000Z","msg":"當年學校tour去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有時間又順路可以去埋一個叫烏鎮嘅地方，真係幾唔錯"},{"pid":"8c358081c4fb1a7af7e4fcd64d901e8394cd6b83","tid":507994,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"西湖可以坐下船<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似20蚊人仔"},{"pid":"b3a38ed137cfe2359f79cfc8ee3cfcc1fe268e3e","tid":507994,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西湖可以坐下船<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似20蚊人仔</blockquote><br />\n住邊度方便d? <br />\n見到有d hotel係西湖隔離,出入會唔會好麻煩? 因為想夜晚行下夜市試下d街頭小食"}]}